tika.dc.description: Looking for a new lease on life? Steer clear of the lukewarm pablum you'll find in most modern self-help books and stick to the classics. Russell Conwell's Every Man His Own University is an amazingly comprehensive guide for any man (or woman!) who needs to make a change—and is willing to put in the work that that entails. Fans of Napoleon Hill's oeuvre will love this book.
